SPIRAL OF LIFE~ Henna art as a Ritual for spiritual healing. A henna experience can be magical on so many levels. Henna rituals have always been an important part of my life since i was a little child and I must say that the day i choose to start my Henna business (named Hand of Fatima) is like the center point of this spiral....so no matter what direction i think i might going....i am always circling or whirling .... going in 360's .... and Henna remains my core ( business) It is my true calling that i'm blessed with...lhmdl....
So many magical moments have taken place this spiral of hennalife... Everything happens for a reason...beautiful encounters with individuals or crazy bridal gigs.....the good and the bad....the successes and the failures....everything is pushing me in this orbit around my hennacore! Henna is the center of my universe!
By the way you already might have seen this piece from me....but I'm reorganizing my instagramfeed...and because it is inpossible to shuffle pics around ( wouldn't that be a brilliant feature?) i'm just gonna repost some of my stuff!
